{
  "texts": [
    "NOVO also improves the document's semantic representation by updating N-gram embeddings.",
    "Later, GLEN [135] uses dynamic lexical DocIDs and follows a two-phase index learning strategy.",
    "First, it assigns DocIDs by extracting keywords from documents using self-supervised signals.",
    "Then, it refines DocIDs by integrating query-document relevance through two loss functions.",
    "During inference, GLEN ranks documents using DocID weights without additional overhead."
  ]
}